08:23.460 --> 08:29.780
You can have communication with teachers through the mail or through the phone, but it's not

08:29.780 --> 08:36.340
like I have classes every day and it's not mandatory to attend to the classes.

08:36.340 --> 08:45.800
What I do is that when I can't attend to the classes, I see the recordings because, of course, you have all of the recordings of the different teachers.

08:45.800 --> 08:55.300
And the university is pretty like cool with that because they understand that people that study virtually is because they have jobs.

08:55.300 --> 09:04.600
So, most of my classmates have jobs and that's why sometimes we don't get the same time to connect, to join the calls.

09:04.760 --> 09:09.980
So, maybe working in a group can be challenging because you never get the times right.

09:09.980 --> 09:17.300
But it's more like remote, I would say that it's more like your own learning, what you do.

09:18.040 --> 09:18.360
Okay.

09:18.540 --> 09:21.320
And yes, you have to be very responsible.

09:22.080 --> 09:22.260
Yeah.

09:22.260 --> 09:24.560
And I have copped with that so far.

09:24.560 --> 09:25.560
Okay.

09:25.560 --> 09:27.940
