09:43.500 --> 09:49.580
I feel good because I have always been really responsible.

09:49.580 --> 09:54.340
I have always been a really independent person.

09:54.340 --> 09:56.780
So, I really appreciate my teachers.

09:57.060 --> 09:58.380
