10:06.580 --> 10:12.320
I started working as an English teacher in one academy that is called SMART.

10:12.320 --> 10:23.380
And since I started working since a very young age, I think that somehow that habit has to be in my life because I have different projects.

10:23.380 --> 10:28.340
As I told you before, I have my own academy now and I study.

10:28.340 --> 10:36.160
So, maybe studying in person would be a little bit more challenging because I would have to take transport and come.

10:36.840 --> 10:41.960
