10:44.980 --> 10:54.980
I like it because the university has really cool content, doing courses all the time, certifications with other universities.

10:55.800 --> 11:08.820
And it's really cool because I feel like I am having my studies without forgetting about my personal and professional projects, which is a really good advantage.

11:09.460 --> 11:10.380
Okay, perfect.

11:10.380 --> 11:15.880
Now, let's talk about a little bit, Tatiana, about your experience as an interpreter.

11:16.360 --> 11:18.100
