18:25.600 --> 18:31.780
Well, definitely, I would, I would like to have these growing opportunities.

18:31.780 --> 18:46.440
I find it really important because as I'm studying these careers, I would like to have maybe the opportunity to, I don't know, have other positions.

18:46.440 --> 18:56.340
Maybe helping people, like, training, for example, because I have had that experience before and I love training.

18:56.520 --> 18:57.500
I love being with people.

18:57.660 --> 19:00.080
So, that is something that really motivates me.

19:00.580 --> 19:04.060
And as a teacher, I like to teach about everything.

19:04.420 --> 19:06.200
And I think I'm really good at that.

19:06.200 --> 19:23.100
And, yes, like, the career opportunities I might have because I find it, like, I find that a company is really valuable when they allow their workers to grow inside the company.

19:23.360 --> 19:24.860
