19:32.480 --> 19:33.920
I like the schedule.

19:34.420 --> 19:35.920
I really like the salary.

19:36.580 --> 19:40.500
I really like the different things I investigated online.

19:40.900 --> 19:42.280
I really like it.

19:42.860 --> 19:50.280
So, I think I find growing opportunities as an important characteristic.

19:50.820 --> 19:50.960
Sure.

19:51.660 --> 19:52.620
Okay, perfect.

19:52.620 --> 20:01.280
So, now, Tatiana, as a part of the process, we will have, like, a second interview with Operation.

20:01.860 --> 20:06.020
In that interview, it's a little different.

20:06.680 --> 20:22.260
In that interview, they're going to perform for you or they're going to be making, sorry, like, some exercise in terms of interpretations, note-taking, and short-hand memory.

20:22.620 --> 20:30.840
So, I want you to be, like, kind of ready for that exercise because it's a little bit, like, complicated.

20:31.440 --> 20:37.760
So, now, I would like to do a little exercise to know how you go in that aspect, okay?

20:39.200 --> 20:44.760
So, I'm going to be saying some sentences in English and also in Spanish.

20:44.760 --> 20:48.280
So, you're going to be translating to the other language, okay?

20:49.360 --> 20:50.140
I didn't hear you.

20:51.440 --> 20:52.480
Oh, sorry.

20:52.720 --> 20:53.720
I don't know what happened.

20:54.120 --> 20:55.380
I didn't hear what you said.

20:55.460 --> 20:56.640
Could you say it one more time?

20:57.320 --> 20:57.520
Yeah.

20:57.620 --> 21:01.080
I'm going to be saying some sentences in both languages.

21:01.080 --> 21:06.460
So, you're going to be interpreting or translating the sentences to the other language, okay?

21:07.640 --> 21:08.740
Okay, sure.

21:08.800 --> 21:09.100
Okay.

21:09.820 --> 21:11.420
Good morning, Mr. Garcia.

21:11.660 --> 21:12.600
